quran[8{c,v,t}:
34,32,barray log kmzoron se kahin ge ke bhala hum ne tum ko hadaayat se jab woh tumahray paas aa chuki thi roka tha? ( nahi ) balkay tum hi gunehgaar they
34,33,aur kamzor log barray logon se kahin ge ( nahi ) balkay ( tumhari ) raat din ki chalon ne ( hamein rok rakha tha ) jab tum hum se kehte they ke hum khuda se kufar karen aur is ka shareek banayen. aur jab woh azaab ko dekhen ge to dil mein pasheman hon ge. aur hum kafiroon ki gardnon mein taoq daal den ge. bas jo amal woh karte they un hi ka un ko badla miley ga
34,34,aur hum ne kisi bastii mein koi darane wala nahi bheja magar wahan ke khush haal logon ne kaha ke jo cheez tum day kar beje gay ho hum is ke qaail nahi
34,35,aur ( yeh bhi ) kehnay lagey ke hum bohat sa maal aur aulaad rakhtay hain aur hum ko azaab nahi hoga
34,36,keh do ke mera rab jis ke liye chahta hai rozi farakh kardaita hai ( aur jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kardaita hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
34,37,aur tumhara maal aur aulaad aisi cheez nahi ke tum ko hamara Maqarrab bana den. haan ( hamara Maqarrab woh hai ) jo imaan laya aur amal naik karta raha. aisay hi logon ko un ke aamaal ke sabab dugna badla miley ga aur woh khatir jama se balakhano+A3888 mein baithy hon ge
34,38,jo log hamari aayton mein koshish karte hain ke hamein hara den woh azaab mein haazir kiye jayen ge
34,39,keh do ke mera perwar-digaar apne bundon mein se jis ke liye chahta hai rozi farakh kardaita hai aur ( jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kardaita hai aur tum jo cheez kharch karo ge woh is ka ( tumhe ) aiwz day ga. aur woh sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai
